metadata.name: Sleeping Cars
metadata.description:
When I lived in London, I loved to explore the streets of the city. The covered cars with victorian-style houses caught my attention. Because the covered cars seemed very aesthetic to me in front of the classic London architecture. However, after this first photo, I started to shoot as a photography project for almost two years.


Camera: Canon 5D Mark III 
Lens: Canon 24-75 mm f2.8 II
Dimensions: 3840 ×  5760
Resolution: 300 dpi
Location: Roseberry Garden, London, UK
Date: 06/06/2018
Edition: 1/1
